title: MisterMusic Show 315 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 315 [192kbps MP3] -120 minutes-



MisterMusic features recent indie and alternative music from this year, and a few classics from the past on this week's show.
Plus the 'Oldie of the Week' was a number 1 hit during August '96 on the US modern rock chart.
It stayed number 1 all month that summer. A major feat for basically a one-hit-wonder.

Broadcasting Weekly and heard on Rock XS Radio...The MisterMusic Show.



Thanks For Listening~Cheers!
